### CCR-024 — WriteGameInfo 프로토콜 (24 필드)
###
### 검증:
### - CC NEW HAND 버튼이 WriteGameInfo 발행 (API-05 §9)
### - 24 필드 스키마 검증 (필수/선택)
### - GameInfoAck / GameInfoRejected 응답
### - 검증 규칙: dealer/sb/bb ∈ active_seats, sb < bb < straddle

@host = http://localhost:8000
@ws_cc = ws://localhost:8000/ws/cc

### 32.1 WriteGameInfo — 정상 (24 필드) (수동 WebSocket)
###
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:8000/ws/cc?table_id=1&token=<jwt>&format=json'
### 다음 메시지 전송:
###
### {
###   "type": "WriteGameInfo",
###   "payload": {
###     "table_id": 1,
###     "hand_id": 248,
###     "dealer_seat": 3,
###     "sb_seat": 4,
###     "bb_seat": 5,
###     "sb_amount": 500,
###     "bb_amount": 1000,
###     "ante_amount": 100,
###     "big_blind_ante": false,
###     "straddle_seats": [6],
###     "straddle_amount": 2000,
###     "blind_structure_id": "wsop-ft-2026-lv42",
###     "blind_level": 42,
###     "current_level_start_ts": "2026-04-10T14:30:00Z",
###     "next_level_start_ts": "2026-04-10T14:50:00Z",
###     "game_type": "no_limit_holdem",
###     "allowed_games": ["nlhe"],
###     "rotation_order": null,
###     "chip_denominations": [100, 500, 1000, 5000, 25000, 100000],
###     "active_seats": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8],
###     "dead_button_mode": true,
###     "run_it_multiple_allowed": true,
###     "bomb_pot_enabled": false,
###     "cap_bb_multiplier": null
###   },
###   "idempotency_key": "uuid-wgi-248",
###   "timestamp": "2026-04-10T14:30:00.123Z",
###   "source_id": "cc-table-1",
###   "message_id": "msg-uuid-wgi-1"
### }
###
### 예상 응답:
### {
###   "type": "GameInfoAck",
###   "payload": {
###     "hand_id": 248,
###     "ready_for_deal": true,
###     "estimated_deal_ready_ts": "2026-04-10T14:30:00.200Z"
###   }
### }

### 32.2 WriteGameInfo — sb_seat이 active_seats에 없음
###
### payload에서 sb_seat = 99, active_seats = [1..8]
###
### 예상 응답:
### {
###   "type": "GameInfoRejected",
###   "payload": {
###     "hand_id": 248,
###     "reason": "VALIDATION_FAILED",
###     "field": "sb_seat",
###     "message": "sb_seat 99 not in active_seats"
###   }
### }

### 32.3 WriteGameInfo — sb_amount >= bb_amount
###
### sb_amount = 1000, bb_amount = 500
###
### 예상: GameInfoRejected
### field: "sb_amount"
### message: "sb_amount must be < bb_amount"

### 32.4 WriteGameInfo — straddle_seats 비어있지 않은데 straddle_amount 누락
###
### straddle_seats = [6], straddle_amount 필드 없음
###
### 예상: GameInfoRejected
### field: "straddle_amount"
### message: "straddle_amount required when straddle_seats is non-empty"

### 32.5 WriteGameInfo — game_type=mix + allowed_games만 1개
###
### game_type = "mix", allowed_games = ["nlhe"]
###
### 예상: GameInfoRejected
### field: "allowed_games"
### message: "mix game requires at least 2 allowed_games"

### 32.6 WriteGameInfo — current_level_start_ts >= next_level_start_ts
###
### current_level_start_ts = "2026-04-10T14:50:00Z"
### next_level_start_ts    = "2026-04-10T14:30:00Z"
###
### 예상: GameInfoRejected
### field: "current_level_start_ts"
### message: "current_level_start_ts must be < next_level_start_ts"
